sql:
SELECT sensor_id
FROM sensors
WHERE location = 'Specific Location';

external_knowledge:
- 'Champion sensors' refers to the sensors with the highest performance rank based on the three criteria; 
- 'Gold medal' average data value means the highest average data value among all sensors; 
- 'Silver medal' high RSSI beacon readings means the highest count of high RSSI readings (RSSI above 50) among all sensors; 
- 'Bronze medal' access counts means the highest count of access events for a sensor among all sensors.
